  "title": "BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT EXECUTIVE (M&A and Digital Marketing)",
  "description": "<p>We're looking for a Strong Salesperson who will be able to acquire clients:</p>\n<p><strong>Sales for Mergers and Acquisitions (LionBrokers)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Sales for Digital Marketing META Lead Generation for the Insurance Industry (Toasty Warm Leads)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Leads will be provided</strong>, our website is up, our pitch decks are solid. We just need</p>\n<p>someone who is really good in sales.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Sales Experience is a MUST HAVE. You will be selling to Business Owners and Insurance Agents</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our culture is a <strong>Good Vibes Only Culture</strong>, no toxicity.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our nice office is at <strong>Clarke Quay The Central.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>SG and PR ONLY. Minimally Diploma.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Payscheme: $2,500 - $3,000 Basic Pay + High 5-7% Commissions</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>About Us:</strong></em></p>\n<p>We are a Group of Companies:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Wise Owl Headhunters - Headhunting</li>\n  <li>Toasty Warm Leads - Digital Marketing</li>\n  <li>LionBrokers - Merger and Acquisitions</li>\n  <li>Trust Bee Media - Press Release</li>\n</ul>",
